summary: I'm a fully bilingual and highly motivated individual with affinity with problem solving and client contact. I enjoy working in a diverse and international environment and I am passionate about handling and resolving clients inquiries. I am friendly, open minded, tech-savvy, and I have a respectful and client centered approach. In my free time I like to engage in sports activities and to explore new places. Coming from Mauritius, but having lived my whole adult life in Canada, I can easily adapt to new contexts.
